longBusinessSummary: Community Redevelopment Inc. operates as a developer of mixed use commercial and multifamily residential communities in the continental United States. The company was formerly known as Crosswind Renewable Energy Corp. and changed its name to Community Redevelopment Inc. in June 2020. Community Redevelopment Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Aventura, Florida.
